Andre Silva has no intentions of staying at Milan as a reserve. His agent Jorge Mendes has been in contact with teams in the Premier League &amp; La Liga. Mendes will be looking at possible swap deals as an option as it will be difficult to get &euro;30-35m for Silva. [<br />
@FabrizioRomano<br />
]

